sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Usuario
    participant Web as React SPA<br/>(RegisterPage)
    participant API as Express API<br/>(/api/auth)
    participant Auth as AuthService
    participant Email as EmailService<br/>(Nodemailer)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>(Neon)
    participant SMTP as Gmail SMTP

    User->>Web: Preenche formulario de registro
    Web->>Web: Valida com Zod (registerSchema)

    alt Validacao falha
        Web-->>User: Exibe erros inline (senha curta, emails diferentes)
    end

    Web->>API: POST /api/auth/register<br/>{name, email, password, confirmPassword}
    API->>API: registerSchema.parse(req.body)

    API->>DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE email = ?
    DB-->>API: Resultado

    alt Email ja existe
        API-->>Web: 400 {message: "Email ja cadastrado"}
        Web-->>User: Exibe erro
    end

    API->>Auth: generateNextUserPlatformId()
    Auth->>DB: SELECT MAX(user_platform_id) FROM users
    DB-->>Auth: USER-XXXX
    Auth-->>API: USER-(XXXX+1)

    API->>Auth: hashPassword(password) [bcrypt, 12 rounds]
    Auth-->>API: hashed password

    API->>DB: INSERT INTO users {id, userPlatformId, email,<br/>password, status: pending_verification}
    DB-->>API: Usuario criado

    API->>Email: generateEmailVerificationToken(userId, email)
    Email-->>API: token (crypto.randomBytes hex)

    API->>Email: sendVerificationEmail(email, token)
    Email->>SMTP: SMTP STARTTLS porta 587<br/>Email HTML com link de verificacao
    SMTP-->>Email: Enviado

    API-->>Web: 201 {message: "Conta criada, verifique seu email"}
    Web-->>User: Redireciona para /registration-confirmation

    Note over User,SMTP: Usuario abre email e clica no link

    User->>Web: Clica no link /verify-email?token=XXX
    Web->>API: POST /api/auth/verify-email {token}

    API->>Email: verifyEmailToken(token)

    alt Token invalido ou expirado
        Email-->>API: null
        API-->>Web: 400 {message: "Token invalido ou expirado"}
        Web-->>User: Exibe erro com opcao de reenviar
    end

    Email-->>API: {userId, email}

    API->>DB: UPDATE users SET email_verified=true,<br/>status=active WHERE id=userId
    DB-->>API: Atualizado

    API-->>Web: 200 {message: "Email verificado com sucesso"}
    Web-->>User: Redireciona para /login
